{"changed":false,"filter":false,"title":"fibonacci.py","tooltip":"/exchange_intro/fibonacci.py","value":"# Fibonacci using variables only\nfib0 = 0\nfib1 = 1\nfib2 = fib1 + fib0\nfib3 = fib2 + fib1\nfib4 = fib3 + fib2\nfib5 = fib4 + fib3\nfib6 = fib5 + fib4\n\nprint(fib6)\n\n\n# Fibonacci using a list and a while-loop\nfib = [0, 1]\nwhile len(fib) < 7:\n    fib_1st_prev = fib[-1]\n    fib_2nd_prev = fib[-2]\n    fib.append(fib_1st_prev + fib_2nd_prev)\n\nprint(fib, fib[6])\n\n\n# Fibonacci using a recurring function\ndef fibf(n):\n    if n == 0:\n        return 0\n    if n == 1:\n        return 1\n\n    return fibf(n - 1) + fibf(n - 2)\n\nprint(fibf(6))\n","undoManager":{"mark":-1,"position":-1,"stack":[]},"ace":{"folds":[],"scrolltop":0,"scrollleft":0,"selection":{"start":{"row":0,"column":0},"end":{"row":0,"column":0},"isBackwards":false},"options":{"guessTabSize":true,"useWrapMode":false,"wrapToView":true},"firstLineState":0},"timestamp":1680690477190}